titl git-commit(1) - message

item Example commit message:
text \begin{lstlisting}[tagsize=2]
	Subject 50 characters or less
	%%
	Remaining text should be wrapped at 72 characters.
	Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit,
	sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore
	magna aliqua.
	\end{lstlisting}

item Why?
	ite2 git log does not handle wrapping
	ite2 git log indents 4 characters at beginning
	ite2 for symmetry add 4 characters at the end
